---
layout: base.njk
title: Web Everything - Home
---

{% from "project-status.njk" import projectStatus %}

<section class="intro">
    <h1>Web Everything Project</h1>
    <p>
        <strong>Web Everything</strong> is an initiative to group a range of standards allowing for better standardization across web libraries.
        Our goal is to create interoperable blocks, behaviors, and tools that work seamlessly with standard web technologies.
    </p>
</section>

<div class="project-grid">
    {% for project in projects %}
    <a href="/projects/{{ project.id }}/" class="project-card">
        <div class="project-icon">
            {% if project.isSvg %}
                <img src="{{ project.icon }}" alt="{{ project.name }} icon" width="48" height="48">
            {% else %}
                {{ project.icon }}
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h2 class="project-title">{{ project.name }}</h2>
        <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
        {{ projectStatus(project.status) }}
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
</div>
